Version 0.3.1:

- ARQ TCP port parametrized
- Add switch to enable gear-shifting (WIP)
- Modulation mode parameter is also used in ARQ mode (when gear-shift is disabled)

Version 0.3:

- New audio subsystem with support to PulseAudio, ALSA, DirectSound and WASAPI
- New shared memory-based simplex modes (RX_SHM, TX_SHM)
- New command line interface with many parameters

Version 0.2.5:

- Implemented more robust modes

Version 0.2:

- Implemented datalink layer - ARQ and Gear-shifting

Version 0.1:

- Implemented physical layer - channel estimation, time sync, filters, OFDM, LDPC
